description: Describes the operating systems that are supported by OpsWorks Stacks.

nested_items.name: OperatingSystems
nested_items.description: Contains information in response to a DescribeOperatingSystems request.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the operating system, such as Amazon Linux 2.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The ID of a supported operating system, such as Amazon Linux 2.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The type of a supported operating system, either Linux or Windows.

nested_items.name: ConfigurationManagers
nested_items.description: Supported configuration manager name and versions for an OpsWorks Stacks operating system.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the configuration manager, which is Chef.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The versions of the configuration manager that are supported by an operating system.

nested_items.name: ReportedName
nested_items.description: A short name for the operating system manufacturer.

nested_items.name: ReportedVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the operating system, including the release and edition, if applicable.

nested_items.name: Supported
nested_items.description: Indicates that an operating system is not supported for new instances.
